    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Hi, I'm Daniel Yang, a bio-pharmaceutical engineer from China.
      <br />
      My knowledge includes:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Pharma Systems</li>
        <li>Pharma Engineering</li>
        <li>Valves</li>
        <li>Aseptic applications</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      There are countless knowledge points in bio-pharmaceutical industry and engineering. 
      I would like to write the roadmap of what I have hear and see during my work.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Hope this will also be useful to you.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
